<plot>A high school student, obsessed with the military and destined for service in the Marines, acquires a video tape - the contents of which depict a government backed murder. Within second of viewing the footage, he finds himself on the run from near-invincible forces. With no one to turn to, he must use the skills he's spent his whole life researching to outsmart the smarter and destroy them before they destroy him.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?237102</url></doc>
